Phoga

Blog tool for Ruby on Rails.


Usage

1. install gem
----------------------------------
$ gem 'phoga', github: 'halenohi/phoga.git'
$ bundle install


2. add configuration
----------------------------------
db/seeds.rb
  Phoga::Engine.load_seed

config/routes.rb
  mount Phoga::Engine, at: '/admin'


3. exec migration & seed
----------------------------------
$ bundle exec rake phoga:install:migrations
$ bundle exec rake db:migrate
$ bundle exec rake db:seed

4. start server
----------------------------------
$ bundle exec rails s
$ open http://localhost:3000
